1
00:00:08,140 --> 00:00:10,040
As for Reika,
I'll figure something out.

2
00:00:10,340 --> 00:00:11,340
So...

3
00:00:11,410 --> 00:00:13,010
about the revenge
and the affair...

4
00:00:13,010 --> 00:00:14,350
please don't tell my dad.

5
00:00:14,610 --> 00:00:17,180
My job is to protect you.

6
00:00:17,520 --> 00:00:19,620
You are not to interfere
with Reika.

7
00:00:22,320 --> 00:00:23,320
For one month.

8
00:00:23,590 --> 00:00:25,960
Make her stop her revenge,
or else...

9
00:00:27,330 --> 00:00:28,760
I'll report everything to President Kurogane.

10
00:00:36,170 --> 00:00:37,170
One month.

11
00:00:37,770 --> 00:00:38,910
Within this one month.

12
00:00:40,270 --> 00:00:42,740
I can let Reika
have her fill of revenge.

13
00:00:43,280 --> 00:00:45,050
I can't just...

14
00:00:45,050 --> 00:00:46,080
submit to Reika's revenge.

15
00:00:46,650 --> 00:00:47,280
Because...

16
00:00:47,450 --> 00:00:48,620
I want Reika...

17
00:00:48,620 --> 00:00:50,020
to get her revenge on me,
again and again.

18
00:00:50,080 --> 00:00:52,220
Letting her get her revenge
is the only...

19
00:00:53,450 --> 00:00:55,720
...way for me to atone.

20
00:01:02,300 --> 00:01:03,300
I'm sorry.

21
00:01:03,500 --> 00:01:04,500
Everything.

22
00:01:05,570 --> 00:01:07,100
I'll take it all.

23
00:01:11,500 --> 00:01:12,500
But...

24
00:01:12,670 --> 00:01:13,870
Who would send something like this...?

25
00:01:13,910 --> 00:01:15,840
Apparently, a hotel employee.

26
00:01:16,280 --> 00:01:17,280
Oh, really?

27
00:01:17,380 --> 00:01:18,910
They said they're a fan of your wife.

28
00:01:18,910 --> 00:01:20,650
and felt sorry for her.

29
00:01:20,650 --> 00:01:22,080
So they pulled the security footage.

30
00:01:22,450 --> 00:01:23,480
I see.

31
00:01:24,380 --> 00:01:25,120
That makes sense.

32
00:01:25,190 --> 00:01:27,190
She has her recipe videos uploaded
to the app our company developed.

33
00:01:27,190 --> 00:01:28,720
They're quite popular.

34
00:01:29,760 --> 00:01:32,760
She's hosted a cooking show before, too.

35
00:01:34,560 --> 00:01:35,560
Speaking of which, are you leaving already?

36
00:01:36,030 --> 00:01:37,230
My apologies.

37
00:01:37,630 --> 00:01:39,130
I still have work to finish.

38
00:01:39,470 --> 00:01:39,800
Aww...

39
00:01:39,800 --> 00:01:41,030
Come on, stay the night.

40
00:01:42,270 --> 00:01:43,700
You could just work from here.

41
00:01:43,700 --> 00:01:45,170
Maybe next time.

42
00:01:47,470 --> 00:01:48,510
Are you defying me?
